  "literalTranslation": {
    "wordAligned": "Did-not you see to the those who exited from their homes and they [were] thousands fear of the death? Then He said to them \"Die!\" then He revived them. Indeed Allah surely is the possessor of bounty upon the people and but most of the people not they thank."
